ys!  By which time, I'm sure, they have maxed out our credit card.  No thanks.  &lt;click&gt;<br><br>&lt;groans&gt; Now I remember why I just hang up on ALL telephone solicitors. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Talcee<br>Shaman of the 40th Season<br>An Elder of <a href=http://www.webhazard.net>The Tears of Veeshan</a><br>(a.k.a. Tigonie Silvanstar)<br>It's Tal-see, not Talc-ie.  It you persist in calling her Talc-ie, I'll name her Talcee Footwear!  ;)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/utovxiarti.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ToV Xiarti</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/14/02 12:31:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=172.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Telephone Scam</span><hr size=1> If you give me your credit card number I'll make sure they never call again.  :P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/utalcee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talcee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tears of Veeshan</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/14/02 12:42:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ftearsofveeshan25764frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=172.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Telephone Scam</span><hr size=1> If you can guess my phone number, I'll give you my credit card.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Talcee<br>Shaman of the 40th Se